  "original_title": "\u0b9f\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0ba9 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9c\u0bc7\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kanchana Wijesekara's announcement to the companies that get fuel by paying dollars",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "Energy Minister Kanchana Wijesekara today announced that any company or industry that can pay in US dollars can open a consumer account with the Sri Lanka Petroleum Corporation to receive weekly guaranteed fuel allocation.",
        "Energy Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said this in a post on his Twitter page.",
        "\u201cThey have to pay a month in advance and will be given on a daily or weekly basis from the 12th. \"Customers who have already paid will get their quota from the 12th,\" he added."
      ],
